description:
Landon and Cassian seemed to be like two peas in a pod. Both of these hotties had a lot of fun playing some basketball together…but distractions were inevitable.
We had to ask Landon the obvious, “Did you see his ass?”
Landon was very excited to answer, “I do see his ass! Let’s go see if we could go give him a good game!”
Needless to say, he did give Cassian a good, hard game.
title: Landon & Cassian: Bareback
